            h1 Privacy Policy
            p.text-muted Effective Date: July 13, 2026

            p Welcome to the personal portfolio and experimental software website of Lior Maman. This website serves as a professional portfolio and a testing environment for software products currently under development ("Beta Services"). By accessing or using this website, you agree to the terms described in this Privacy Policy.

            hr

            h3 1. Beta Status & No Business Relationship

            p This website is operated as a personal portfolio and software development project. Certain features may be experimental, incomplete, or subject to change without notice.

            p All services are provided on an "AS-IS" and "AS-AVAILABLE" basis without warranties of any kind, express or implied.

            hr

            h3 2. No User Accounts & Data Minimization

            p At this stage, we do not create user accounts, maintain user profiles, or intentionally collect personally identifiable information.

            ul
                li #[strong No Registration:] Users are not required to create an account.
                li #[strong No Personal Profiles:] We do not maintain personal user records.
                li #[strong Session Inputs:] Information entered into demo tools is processed temporarily to generate results and is not intended to be linked to a user's identity.

            hr

            h3 3. Technical Data & Hosting Logs

            p Our hosting providers and infrastructure services may automatically collect limited technical information necessary for security, maintenance, and performance monitoring.

            ul
                li Browser type
                li Device information
                li IP address
                li Access timestamps
                li Error and diagnostic logs

            p This information is used solely for technical operations, security, and troubleshooting.

            hr

            h3 4. Third-Party Service Providers

            p Certain features may utilize third-party service providers, including AI services, cloud infrastructure providers, analytics services, or financial data providers.

            p Information submitted through these features may be transmitted temporarily to those providers for processing. Users should avoid submitting confidential, proprietary, financial account, or other sensitive information.

            hr

            h3 5. Cookies & Local Storage

            p This website may use essential cookies or browser local storage strictly for technical functionality and user experience improvements.

            ul
                li Theme preferences
                li Interface settings
                li Temporary session functionality

            p We do not use advertising cookies or behavioral tracking technologies.

            hr

            h3 6. Financial Disclaimer

            p Any financial information, analytics, charts, market data, forecasts, insights, simulations, or AI-generated content presented on this website are provided solely for informational, educational, and demonstration purposes.

            p Nothing on this website constitutes financial, investment, legal, accounting, tax, or professional advice.

            p Users are solely responsible for evaluating information and making their own decisions. You should consult qualified professionals before making investment or financial decisions.

            p Lior Maman shall not be responsible for any losses, damages, or consequences arising from reliance on information provided through this website.

            hr

            h3 7. Limitation of Liability

            p To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Lior Maman shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or punitive damages arising from the use of this website or any Beta Services.

            p This includes, but is not limited to, loss of data, financial losses, service interruptions, inaccuracies, or system downtime.

            hr

            h3 8. Changes to This Policy

            p This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically as the project evolves and new functionality is introduced.

            p Continued use of the website following any updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.

            hr

            h3 9. Contact

            p For questions regarding this Privacy Policy or the website, please use the contact methods provided on the main website.

